profile: We are a full service design & remodeling company located in Halifax, NS. From concept to completion we take care of the design process, material selections & construction/build for home improvement projects such as; kitchen remodels, bathroom remodels, home additions, basement renovations, exterior renovations and full home remodels. Our projects are protected by two separate guarantees, constituting the most expansive customer protection plan in the industry.
